  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It is an VR adventure level-based game featuring FPS, roguelite elements. <br></li><li>The player plays an adventurer, who explores the ancient Egyptian tombs in a parallel world, and goes deep into the huge underground world to find the legendary secret treasure.<br></li><li>Every level is generated randomly, each new restart after each failure is a brand-new experience. <br></li><li>In each expedition, players can find a variety of different weapons, as well as artifacts with special abilities. The combination of different weapons and artifacts will  will lead different game strategies and bring unique customs clearance experience.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=492 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various Weapons:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic pistols, Scorpion Submachine Gun, SawnOff Shotgun, etc.<br></li><li>Crazy Flamethrowers, Explosive Crossbows, Fuel Rod Guns, etc.<br></li><li>Plasma pistol, Okan Laser, Gravity Gun, etc.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=494 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful ancient Artifacts:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mask of Osiris - Weaking the attacker.<br></li><li>Horus's Wristband - Causing bullet time.<br></li><li>Ankh' Guardian - Providing blood sucking ability.<br></li><li>Element Ring - Debuffing the monsters with negative effect, such as freezing, petrifying and burning.<br></li><li>And so on.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monsters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Slowly moving mummies.<br></li><li>The rampaging cemetery guards.<br></li><li>Crowds of scarabs.<br></li><li>Cannibal scorpions that corrode everything.<br></li><li>The huge statue of Anubis.<br></li><li>The powerful and terrible Pharaohs.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>And so on.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Levels</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=498 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><a href=\"mailto:MAIL：special@xrlinkup.com\">MAIL：special@xrlinkup.com</a>",
